r, higher paid, roles at the office show a greater proportion of men than women. However, we are confident that everyone who works for F.Hinds is being paid equally for doing equivalent jobs.  Hourly Rate Women's hourly rate is 36.2% lower (mean) Women's hourly rate is 13.7% lower (median)   Pay Quartiles Top quartile: Men 48.4% Women 51.6% Upper middle quartile: Men 10.3% Women 89.7% Lower middle quartile: Men 12.1% Women 87.9% Lower quartile: Men 23.0% Women 77.0%   Bonus Pay Men's bonus pay is: 50.9% higher (mean) 58.1% higher (median)  Who received bonus pay: 29.7% of men 10.2% of women     About Us  About Us Our History Why buy from F.Hinds? Returns & Exchanges Delivery Charges FAQs Terms & Conditions Ethical Diamond Trading Responsible Jewellery Council National Association of Jewellers Modern Slavery Statement Privacy Policy Cookie Policy Charity Policy Gender Pay Gap Affiliates Sale Information                    About Us About Us Our History Why buy from F.Hinds? Returns Delivery Charges Terms & Conditions Careers Ethical Diamond Trading Responsible Jewellery Council The NAJ Affiliates Blog Services Customer Services Click & Collect Gift Cards Leave a Review Sign up to our Newsletter Request a Catalogue Gold for Cash Repair Service Ear Piercing Valuations Bespoke Design Service Sitemap Follow Us Facebook Twitter Instagram   Ways to Pay          Back to Top   Back to Top                 Copyright © F.Hinds 1997 - 2018. ecommerce by red  F.Hinds Limited London 24 Park Road, Uxbridge, Middlesex UB8 1NH 149328 tel:0800 0344637 onlinesales@fhinds.co.uk          This site uses cookies and by using the site you are consenting to this. Find out why we use cookies and how to manage your settings. Full details can be found here .                          